update instruction withthis error - That Tailscale “Setup Failed – 0x80072f7d (Unspecified error)” on Windows is actually a very common installer failure, and it’s usually not Tailscale itself being broken. It’s almost always a Windows networking / security / certificate issue.The fix that works most of the time (Windows TLS reset)
3️⃣ Reset Windows TLS & crypto settings

This error often means Windows TLS is misconfigured.

Press Win + R

Type:

inetcpl.cpl

Go to Advanced tab

Scroll to Security

✅ Make sure these are checked:

Use TLS 1.2

Use TLS 1.3 (if present)

❌ Uncheck:

SSL 3.0

TLS 1.0

TLS 1.1

Click Apply → OK

Reboot

Update